item.title: Best Online Plagiarism Checkers that are Free
item.description: Plagiarism in the online world is the art of stealing others content without the copyright holder’s permission. It is bad for bloggers because duplicate content can affect their blog’s search engine visibility. Bloggers are not the only professionals worried about Plagiarism. Teachers always fear that their students might copy the homework from any one of the billions of sites available in Google’s search index. If you think that your hard work has been copied or if you’re a teacher who wants to check the genuineness of student’s homework, use the below tools to find all websites that have duplicate content.
